[normal](2) In paragraph 5 (committees) at the end insert–
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]              
[normal]“(4) But the Audit Committee (or, if there is no committee with that title, any committee established for audit purposes) may include up to two persons who are not members of the Commission (“independent members”); and–
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](a)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]a person may not be appointed as an independent member if the person would be ineligible for appointment as an ordinary member under paragraph 1(3), and
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](b)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]an independent member may do anything that another member can do (including chairing the committee).”
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](3) In paragraph 12 (five-year plan)–
